data.title: Add Relationship
data.text: Felicia Farr was born on October 4, 1932 in Westchester County, New York, USA as Olive Felicia Dines. She is an actress, known for Charley Varrick (1973), 3:10 to Yuma (1957) and Kiss Me, Stupid (1964). She was previously married to Jack Lemmon and Lee Farr. She is the daughter of Sylvia (Schwartz) and Max Dines. Her parents were of Russian Jewish and Romanian Jewish descent.
